                        <interp inst="t18460223-672-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">of an Assault.</hi> Aged 73.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor. 
